OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784225905
OL,3,C'Menace' chocolate thief jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing from Waterstones and Hotel
OL,5,CChocolat
OL,7,FA sweet-toothed thief has been given
OL,8,F16 weeks behind bars for stealing
OL,9,Fchocolate from a Waterstones in
OL,10,FNottingham.
OL,12,FSecurity camera footage shows her
OL,13,Ftaking a tote bag from the shelf
OL,14,Fbefore filling it with #156 of
OL,15,Fchocolate.
OL,17,FCharlotte Jones of Hartley Road was
OL,18,Falready banned from some shops across
OL,19,Fthe city centre because of her
OL,20,Fpersistent offending.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
