PN,34102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784225905
OL,3,C'Menace' chocolate thief jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing from Waterstones and Hotel
OL,5,CChocolat
OL,7,FShe'd received an 18-week sentence,
OL,8,Fsuspended for 12 months in January
OL,9,Fafter she stole more than #800 of
OL,10,Fconfectionery from Hotel Chocolat over
OL,11,Fmultiple trips.
OL,13,FThe 36-year-old took boxes of
OL,14,Fchocolate and gift sets from the shop
OL,15,Fin Albert Street.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784225905
OL,3,C'Menace' chocolate thief jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing from Waterstones and Hotel
OL,5,CChocolat
OL,7,FShe was then given a Criminal
OL,8,FBehaviour Order, which meant she would
OL,9,Fbe recalled to prison if she breached
OL,10,Fthe terms of the order - which she did
OL,11,Fduring her theft from Waterstones in
OL,12,FBridlesmith Gate in June.
OL,14,FAppearing at Nottingham Magistrates
OL,15,FCourt on 14 July, Jones was given a 16-
OL,16,Fweek prison sentence after pleading
OL,17,Fguilty.
OL,19,FShe was also ordered to pay #156.79 in
OL,20,Fcompensation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784225905
OL,3,C'Menace' chocolate thief jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing from Waterstones and Hotel
OL,5,CChocolat
OL,7,FSergeant Jono Pothecary for
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police said: "Jones is
OL,9,Fa menace who has caused absolute
OL,10,Fmisery to the shops she has targeted,
OL,11,Fincluding Hotel Chocolat and
OL,12,FWaterstones.
OL,14,F"Having Jones off the streets should
OL,15,Fbe welcomed by Nottingham stores who
OL,16,Fhad to endure her persistent offending.
OL,18,F"I hope this spell behind bars might
OL,19,Factually make her think about her
OL,20,Factions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
