CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784225905
OL,3,C'Menace' chocolate thief jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing from Waterstones and Hotel
OL,5,CChocolat
OL,7,F"She has shown no regard whatsoever
OL,8,Ffor the impact her offending has
OL,9,Fcaused those trying to do an honest
OL,10,Fday's work."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
